  <div class="terms-content">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <h2>TERMS</h2>
      <h4>NET PRICING</h4>
      <p>Net Pricing applies to designers and businesses.</p>
      <p>Net pricing is not applicable for LUCCA HOME ecommerce products</p>
      <p>To qualify for Net pricing in retail location, business must Have a valid resale certificate for a design or related enterprise.</p>
      <h4>ORDER CONFIRMATION</h4>
      <p>Once we receive your ecommerce order, you will receive a confirmation with the following information: </p>
      <p>•  Availability of items you have ordered. </p>
      <p>• If item is available, you will be provided list of shippers and will arrange shipping. Lucca does not endorse any shipper and is not responsible for shipping quotes or liability related to goods once they leave the Lucca Warehouse or retail location. </p>
      <p>In-stock LUCCA HOME ecommerce items are processed and shipped within 7-10 business days. </p>
      <p>For Custom Order lead times, see your Custom Order agreement and contact the LUCCA store magaer where items were purchased. </p>
      <h4>SHIPPING FOR ECOMMERCE</h4>
      <p>RESIDENTIAL SMALL PACKAGE GROUND </p>
      <p>• 20% of total invoice ($25 min)</p>
      <p>DELIVERY COMPANY/CLIENT PICKUP </p>
      <p>• On site pickup at our warehouse in Los Angeles, CA only. </p>
      <p>• Appointments must be scheduled at least 48 hours in advance. </p>
      <p>• Payment must be processed and cleared prior to making a pickup appointment. </p>
      <p>LUCCA HOME ecommerce products will ship via UPS when possible. </p>
      <p>For appointments or information on a shipment, email <a href="mailto:shipping@luccahome.com">shipping@luccahome.com</a></p>
      <h4>PAYMENT POLICIES</h4>
      <p>￼For domestic sales, we accept all major credit cards, checks, ACH payments and wires. For international orders, we only accept credit cards and wires. Orders paid for by credit card ship immediately while those paid for by check ship once the check has cleared. Wire transfers are subject to a $25 wire transfer fee. </p>
      <p>Orders cannot be processed without payment information. Payment with shipping is due in full at the time of order. We only hold merchandise once credit card information or payment via check has cleared.</p>
      <h4>RETURNS / EXCHANGES</h4>
      <p>We do not accept cancellations, returns or exchanges and ask that you choose wisely! We strongly advise that you see product in person. </p>
      <h4>DAMAGES</h4>
      <p>LUCCA has developed a very thorough level of quality control which includes inspections at every point of production, and packaging. Nevertheless, problems occasionally do occur.</p>
      <p>Upon receiving your shipment, please do the following: </p>
      <p>￼• If you notice obvious box damage, note the damage on the delivery receipt the driver gives you to sign and notify driver of the damage immediately and take photos</p>
      <p>• Inspect the product noting any damage on the delivery receipt, and take photos</p>
      <p>• Contact the shippers claim department immediately and provide us with photos of all damaged products and photos of any damaged boxing and packaging materials </p>
      <p>• Keep all of the original packaging material </p>
      <p>The customer responsible for choosing, hiring and dealing with the shipping of items purchased through LUCCA. IF damage to items occurs, the customers must work with the shipper to deal with any claims of damage. LUCCA will not accept any liability, Lucca will not accept returns or exchanges of items damaged by shipper.</p>
      <h4>CRAFTSMANSHIP</h4>
      <p>LUCCA products are crafted using natural materials and heritage techniques, there are no chemicals used. Natural materials and antiques, have variations such as imperfections, knots or graining, and may exhibit characteristic signs of age or an artist’s hand. We consider these the proud hallmarks of rarity, natural materials and of hand-craftsmanship which contribute to the uniqueness and beauty of our pieces.</p>
      <p>Our items are designed and produced in California, colors may not match across different lines or collections. Every piece is made by hand. Additionally, as we continuously change our designs and finishes, items from different production runs may vary slightly from each other.</p>
